Package: procdump-dev
Version: @PROJECT_VERSION_MAJOR@.@PROJECT_VERSION_MINOR@.@PROJECT_VERSION_PATCH@
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: Sysinternals <syssite@microsoft.com>
Section: libdevel
Description: Development files for ProcDump (static library and headers)
 This package contains the static library (libprocdump.a) and C header
 (ProcDumpLib.h) used to link against ProcDump and generate process core
 dumps on demand from your own programs.
Depends: zlib1g
License: MIT
